data.description: Welcome to the perfect combination of functional living space and outdoor enjoyment! This style of home features multiple levels that create distinct living areas, providing a sense of privacy and separation while maintaining an open and connected atmosphere. The main level encompasses the primary living areas with lots of natural light. The sizable level fenced backyard offers an ample space for outdoor activities, entertaining, or a tranquil retreat. This property offers a harmonious blend, unique design, and abundant outdoor space making it an appealing choice for those seeking a comfortable home in a welcoming and active community. No showings until Sunday,  November 26th. Open house 1-3pm on November 26th, 2023.
